    PLAN[Plan or failure event\n(name, version, tags)] --> ENQ[Enqueue retry\n(package, version, tags, recipes)]
    UI[UI/API enqueue action] --> ENQ
    ENQ --> FILE[retry queue backend\nfile / Redis / Kafka]
    FILE --> LIST[List queue]
    FILE --> CLEAR[Clear queue]
    FILE --> POP[Pop batch for worker]
    POP --> WORKER[Go worker (Podman)\nrefinery-build per job\nposts logs/manifest]
    LIST --> UI
    CLEAR --> UI
